\\subsection{1.1 / DATA COMMUNICATIONS AND NETWORKING FOR TODAY'S ENTERPRISE}
\\begin{figure}[htbp]
\\centering
\\includegraphics[width=\\textwidth]{_page_0_Figure_2.jpeg}
