\\begin{enumerate}
    \\item The first bit is a framing bit, used for synchronization.
    \\item Voice channels:
    \\begin{itemize}
        \\item 8-bit PCM used on five of six frames.
        \\item 7-bit PCM used on every sixth frame; bit 8 of each channel is a signaling bit.
    \\end{itemize}
