    \\includegraphics[width=0.8\\textwidth]{_page_0_Figure_9.jpeg}
    \\caption{Illustration of Slow Start and Congestion Avoidance}
    \\label{fig:slowstart}
\\end{figure}

\\textsuperscript{5} Kleinrock refers to this phenomenon as the long-tail effect during a rush-hour period. See Sections 2.7 and 2.10 of [KLEI76] for a detailed discussion.

